{
  "title": "TileMapObject",
  "description": "A format-independent map object. The geometry kind is the discriminant; narrow on `kind` to read shape-specific fields. Template objects are not yet represented. The optional property-shape parameter `P` lets typed accessors (see ObjectLayer.byType) narrow `properties` to a developer-declared schema. It defaults to the generic TileProperties bag, so the plain `TileMapObject` form is unchanged.",
